    "updated_at": "2014-06-17T01:29:41Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Good points on not getting too clever.  Having said that, I think this approach of adding a simple explanatory statement (_without_ hiding the traceback or otherwise obscuring the problem, as @minrk  pointed out in his closed PR), is a good idea.  It's low cost, and if it helps us steer a few users every now and then away from a trap that may discourage them, all the better.\n\nThere's no such thing as \"too friendly/easy installation\", or at least we're still a galaxy away from that.\n"
