    "updated_at": "2014-06-18T00:37:51Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "My objection is that we have no way of knowing that the error is because they need to install that module, as opposed to any of the other problems that might cause an ImportError, and it seems strange to do it for only a couple of our many imports of third party dependencies.\n\nHowever, I hear what you're saying about nitpicks, and I won't comment any more on this issue. I will unsubscribe from notifications so I'm not tempted to. ;-)\n"
